The whole point of the sport is to win fights through KO, TKO, Submission or Decision.. since neither guy accomplished the first 3 then we have to leave it at the decision. The decision is Izzy won. Paulo Costa has a big chance of winning the title from izzy.. so hopefully we can see PC & YR sometime in the future.
